X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Davis": "https://visitdavis.org/event/2nd-friday-artabout-at-the-pence-gallery-13/", "Visityolo Event": "https://visityolo.com/event/2nd-friday-artabout-at-the-pence-gallery-15/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Davis": "https://visitdavis.org/event/2nd-friday-artabout-at-the-pence-gallery-13/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitdavis
X-SOURCE:Visit Davis, Visityolo Event
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T210000
DTSTAMP:20260406T180712
CREATED:20260402T173022Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260406T160146Z
UID:10002820-1775844000-1775854800@visitdavis.org
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout at the Pence Gallery
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Pence Gallery in Davis for our 2nd Friday ArtAbout reception on April 10\, 6-9 PM. Enjoy browsing multiple art exhibits\, a complimentary wine tasting by Fjord Oak Winery\, an art-themed scavenger hunt\, and live folk music by Plain Folk in the courtyard (6-8 PM). Free admission! \nThe Abstract Language of Ceramics | Apr. 10 – Jun. 3\nThis exhibit features the work of ceramic artists Karyn Gabriel\, Mark Goudy\, Kris Marubayashi\, Liza Riddle\, and Laura Van Duren. Together\, these artists create striking geometric and biomorphic forms that underline their pursuit of simple forms inspired by nature. \nAssorted Flavors: Pence Member Exhibit | Mar. 13 – Apr. 16\nOur 2nd annual non-juried exhibit celebrates the creativity and talent of our organization’s supporters\, showcasing work in different media by 40 Pence Members. \nBarbara Prodaniuk: Myths in Mud | Mar. 13 – Apr. 26\nThe ceramic artist’s work is inspired by the forest\, meadows\, and waterways surrounding the Truckee area. She explores the stories carried by the creatures and artifacts found in these environments through layered surfaces\, organic textures\, and sculpted imagery. \nJulie Bernadeth Crumb: Stairway Show | Apr. 4 – May 17\nView the artist’s collection of work featured along the stairway. \nScavenger Hunt: Join us for a fun\, art-themed scavenger hunt at the Pence during the 2nd Friday ArtAbout. Complete all of the clues by exploring our exhibits for the chance to win a special prize. \n— \nVisit the Pence and other venues in Downtown Davis for the 2nd Friday ArtAbout artwalk. We will have printed ArtAbout guides available that week. Follow the ArtAbout’s Facebook page for more information: https://www.facebook.com/davisartabout. \nImages:\nMark Goudy\, “Flux Series”\nJoseph Bellacera\, “Equations of the Five Dimensions”\nBarbara Prodaniuk\, “Raven Goddess” (detail)
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/2nd-friday-artabout-at-the-pence-gallery-13/
LOCATION:Pence Gallery\, 212 D Street\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Pence-Reception-Banners-1-gSHB5m.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencesocialmedia@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
